WEBVTT

00:02.144 --> 00:04.856
The body had feet, all right,
and the feet had sneakers.

00:04.880 --> 00:06.776
- Body have no feet.
- We both saw 'em.

00:06.800 --> 00:10.168
- Some people learn the hard way.
- You are no man right now.

00:12.616 --> 00:14.280
How did you get in here?

00:14.384 --> 00:16.408
Where is Ivan?!

00:17.488 --> 00:19.240
Get out of here. Don't come back!

00:19.328 --> 00:20.656
No, look out, look out!

00:23.960 --> 00:26.712
This gate is the only thing standing
between me and jail.

00:26.736 --> 00:30.120
Uh, how do you know that?
We haven't found the church yet.

00:36.300 --> 00:38.520
I think I'm falling in love.

00:38.680 --> 00:39.920
With who?

00:40.670 --> 00:42.770
- Florida.
- Florida?

00:43.150 --> 00:46.984
If you had a good idea,
it would die of loneliness.

00:47.610 --> 00:49.071
I guess you're gonna tell me

00:49.072 --> 00:52.350
Florida is young, smart,
and smokin',

00:52.420 --> 00:54.960
and I'm old, dumb,
and don't have a real job,

00:55.000 --> 00:56.936
and a woman like Florida can
never fall in love

00:56.960 --> 00:58.472
with a loser like me.

00:59.664 --> 01:01.152
Look down.

01:01.528 --> 01:03.290
See all those fools down there?

01:03.528 --> 01:06.520
You and me, we ain't nothin'
like them, Hap.

01:08.200 --> 01:09.720
I love you, man.

01:09.744 --> 01:11.128
Love you, too, Hap.

01:15.680 --> 01:17.072
Collins.

01:18.392 --> 01:20.656
Your turn on the dance floor.

01:23.344 --> 01:25.768
Wake up, asshole.

01:26.168 --> 01:27.448
Get dressed.

01:34.490 --> 01:35.790
You're lucky.

01:35.806 --> 01:39.546
We got Mr. Bobby Joe Soothe
in here; serenade you.

01:40.856 --> 01:42.600
Thought they had rules

01:43.300 --> 01:46.504
about inmates having shit
they could hang themselves with.

01:46.520 --> 01:49.488
Ah, my Bobby Joe wouldn't
do that.

01:49.512 --> 01:51.440
Turn around.

