02:03.928 --> 02:06.928
What the hell they got you
in here for now?

02:08.344 --> 02:09.592
Arson.

02:12.248 --> 02:13.728
You?

02:14.470 --> 02:16.000
Kidnappin'.

02:19.440 --> 02:20.770
Who?

02:21.088 --> 02:22.520
Beau Otis.

02:27.264 --> 02:29.864
You know that Beau Otis is
an epileptic?

02:31.240 --> 02:32.648
Didn't know.

02:33.080 --> 02:34.990
Don't care.

